<codeline><highlight class="normal">#<sp/>helios::engine::runtime::spawn::events</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Spawn-related<sp/>events<sp/>for<sp/>cross-frame<sp/>communication.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Overview</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>module<sp/>provides<sp/>events<sp/>that<sp/>are<sp/>pushed<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>frame<sp/>event<sp/>bus<sp/>to<sp/>enable<sp/>communication<sp/>between<sp/>the<sp/>spawn<sp/>system<sp/>and<sp/>the<sp/>scheduling<sp/>system.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Key<sp/>Classes</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>Class<sp/>|<sp/>Purpose<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|-------|---------|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">|<sp/>`SpawnPlanCommandExecutedEvent`<sp/>|<sp/>Signals<sp/>that<sp/>a<sp/>spawn<sp/>plan<sp/>command<sp/>was<sp/>executed<sp/>|</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">##<sp/>Usage</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Events<sp/>are<sp/>pushed<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>SpawnManager<sp/>after<sp/>processing<sp/>spawn<sp/>commands:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```cpp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>In<sp/>SpawnManager::flush()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">updateContext.pushFrame&lt;SpawnPlanCommandExecutedEvent&gt;(</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>spawnRuleId,<sp/>actualSpawnCount</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">Events<sp/>are<sp/>read<sp/>by<sp/>the<sp/>GameObjectSpawnSystem<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>next<sp/>frame:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```cpp</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">//<sp/>In<sp/>GameObjectSpawnSystem::update()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">for<sp/>(const<sp/>auto&amp;<sp/>evt<sp/>:<sp/>updateContext.readFrame&lt;SpawnPlanCommandExecutedEvent&gt;())<sp/>{</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>spawnScheduler_-&gt;commit(evt.spawnRuleId,<sp/>evt.spawnCount);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">}</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal">```</highlight></codeline>
<codeline></codeline>
